"title": "8625: worship, acceptable attitudes in",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8625",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>True worship is not the mechanical repetition of rituals, but should be wholehearted and reverent. It should be based upon trustful and obedient lives, in that obedience is itself to be seen as an act of worship.</p>\n<h2>Worship should be in accordance with God's commands</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen22:2\">GEN 22:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen12:1\">GEN 12:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen12:7-Gen12:8\">GEN 12:7–12:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut30:16-Deut30:20\">DEU 30:16–30:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam15:22\">1SA 15:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps40:6-Ps40:8\">PSA 40:6–40:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer7:2\">JER 7:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan3:28\">DAN 3:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:2\">ACT 13:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:1\">ROM 12:1</a></p>\n<h2>Worship should not be mechanical</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John4:23-John4:24\">JHN 4:23–4:24</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:1\">HEB 10:1</a></p>\n<h2>Worship should give God the honour due to him</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr16:29\">1CH 16:29</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps96:8-Ps96:9\">PSA 96:8–96:9</a></p>\n<h2>Worship of mere human devising is unacceptable</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa29:13\">ISA 29:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev10:1\">LEV 10:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:7-Matt15:9\">MAT 15:7–15:9</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark7:6-Mark7:7\">MRK 7:6–7:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil3:3\">PHP 3:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:23\">COL 2:23</a></p>\n<h2>Worship should be orderly and reverent</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor14:40\">1CO 14:40</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr16:37-1Chr16:42\">1CH 16:37–16:42</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs18:30-1Kgs18:39\">1KI 18:30–18:39</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor14:26\">1CO 14:26</a></p>\n<h2>Worship should be grounded in godly and obedient living</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic6:6-Mic6:8\">MIC 6:6–6:8</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:1\">ROM 12:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps15:1-Ps15:5\">PSA 15:1–15:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps24:3-Ps24:4\">PSA 24:3–24:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim2:10\">1TI 2:10</a></p>\n<h2>The proper attitude of worshippers</h2>\n<h3>Preparation for worship</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor11:28\">1CO 11:28</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev16:3-Lev16:4\">LEV 16:3–16:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam12:20\">2SA 12:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr7:1\">2CH 7:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt2:11\">MAT 2:11</a></p>\n<h3>Wholeheartedness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut6:5\">DEU 6:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod34:14\">EXO 34:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut10:12\">DEU 10:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh22:5\">JOS 22:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam12:24\">1SA 12:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps27:4\">PSA 27:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt22:37\">MAT 22:37</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:30\">MRK 12:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:27\">LUK 10:27</a></p>\n<h3>Confidence in approaching God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:22-Heb10:23\">HEB 10:22–10:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen4:4\">GEN 4:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas4:8\">JAS 4:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb7:19\">HEB 7:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:4\">HEB 11:4</a></p>",
